title: Robocop Versus The Terminator
description:
Robocop Versus The Terminator is a four-issue comic book crossover limited series published in 1992. It was written by Frank Miller and drawn by Walt Simonson. Details that were cut out of both the scripts that Frank Miller wrote for Robocop 2 and Robocop 3, mainly the detail on Robocop's brain, were used in the story.

Published by Dark Horse Comics.
